title: Dinesh D'Souza Is Our Guest, so This Is Probably Blocked | Daily Best of May 20 | Rick & Bubba
description:
Election fraud is the most censored subject in America today. Dinesh D'Souza joins us to discuss the reaction to his latest project, "2000 Mules." Last time we had him on, we were flagged with warning labels all across our social media, so don't be surprised if the only place you can find this is BlazeTV. In other news, the college football world is reeling in the aftermath of Nick Saban speaking out against Jimbo Fisher and Texas A&M. And lastly, why is the price of gas so high? Joe Biden's answer: Joe Biden.
